Contents:

Note: Komodo is a chess engine and not a chess GUI and thus requires the use
of a third party Graphical User Interface as most modern chess engines
do. For instance:

* Arena (http://www.playwitharena.com/)
* Tarrasch (http://www.triplehappy.com/)
